# 🧪 Libreview Credentials (Optional)
# Use these only if you want to provide default IDs for your specific account.
# Otherwise, the app will dynamically fetch these upon login.

# The 64-character SHA256 hash of your account's plain User ID.
# LIBREVIEW_ACCOUNT_ID_HASH=ff08d9e2...

# The patient identifier for the data stream.
# LIBREVIEW_CONNECTION_ID=f096bccd-...
